    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tu Karrâ eﬅt prett ta-\nweem Eenaidneefeemi / un taſ\nKUNGS nodohs wiꞥſchus tawa\nRohkâ / ka tu wiꞥſchu Substitus\nZeetuma noweddi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu redſeki ſtarp teem\nSubſtiteem weeni ſkatſtu See-\nwu/ un tu gribbeſi wiꞥſchu/ ta ka\ntu wiꞥſchu par Seewu nem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs tew wiꞥſchu ta-\ntawâ Namma weſt / un laid wiꞥſcha\nfawu Galwn apzehrpi/un fuwus\nNaggus apgraisa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tad laid wiꞥſcha fawas\nZeetuma Drehbes ſew nowelk/ un\ntawâ Namma fehd / un fawu\nTehwu/ un fawu Mahti weenu\nMehneſi apraud/un pehz to buhs\ntew pee wiꞥſkas eet / un wiꞥſcai\npar lauſatu Draugu buht / un\nwiꞥſka laid tawa Seewa irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ja wiꞥſka tew ne patihſ/\ntad warr tu wiꞥſchu atlaift / fur\nwiꞥſka patti grib / bet par Nau-\ndu tew ne buhs wiꞥſchu pahrdoht/\nneds ar wiꞥſnas Naudu pelniht/\ntapehz ka tu wiꞥſchu effi paſeimojs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad kadham Wihran di-\nwi Seewas buhs/weena ko wiꞥſch\nmihte/un ohtra/ko wiꞥſch eenihſt/\nun ta Mihkota lihſ ar tahs / ko\nwiꞥſch eenihſt Dehlus irr dſemdej-\nſi/ un tas Pirmdſintajs tai pee-\nDerr/ ko wiꞥſch eenihſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tai Deenâ / kad wiꞥſch\nfaweem Dehleem par Jhpaschu-\nmu iſdohs/ kas wiꞥſnam irr/ tad\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥſnam buhs tah\nEenihdetas Dehlu atſihcees/ do-\ndams wiꞥſnam to diwkahrtig\nTeeſu/ no wiﬀa/ kas pee wiꞥſ-\natraſts tohp / jo tas irr wiꞥſ-\npirmajs Spehks/ ta Pirmdſint-\nbas-Teefa tam peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad kadham Wihran ween\npahrgalwigſ un neklaufis Dehl\nirr / ne klaufidams fawa Tehw-\nBalkfnet/ un tee wiꞥſchu irr pahr-\nmahziſchi/un wiꞥſch tomehr teen\nne klaufihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs wiꞥſcha Tehwan\nun wiꞥſcha Mahtei to ſagrahbt/un\nwiꞥſchu ahra weſt pee fawa Pils-\nfahta Wezzajeem / un pee fawa\nWeetas Wahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un teem buhs uſ fawa Pils-\nfahta Wezzajeem fazzibt : Schi-\nmuhſu Dehls irr pahrgalwigſ un\nneklaufigſ/wiꞥſch ne klaufa muh-\nfu Balkfnet / wiꞥſch irr wcene\nRihjejs un Plihtetajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs wiﬀeem wiꞥſcha\nPilsfahta Landim to ar Akini-\nxeem nonichtaht/ ka tas mirſt/ ta-\nbuhs teem to Launu no tawas\nWiddus atnemt/ ka wife Israels\nto dfird/un bihſtahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja kas kadhu Grehku-\ndarriſs / zaur ko wiꞥſch to Nahw-\nirr pelnijs/un tas nokaujamês irr /\nun tu wiꞥſchu pee kadhu Kohku-\npakahrti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad laid wiꞥſcha nomirru-\n"
    }
  ],
